name: Technomagical
body:
## Welcome!
Welcome to the Technomagical site!
Here you'll find information on the new Minecraft mod.

## Help out!
Join the team! Fork the repo hedgehog1029/technomagical and then change whatever. Then send a pull request detailing what you've changed and I'll merge if the changes are good!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
